"MsoNormal" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;">②二人が同居し、共同生活において互いに責任を持って協力し、その他共<span lang="EN-US" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;"><o:p style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;"></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;">同生活に必要な費用を分担する義務を負うこと<span lang="EN-US" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;"><o:p style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;"></o:p></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span lang="EN-US" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><table class="MsoTableGrid" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;"><tbody style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;"><td width="566" colspan="3" valign="top" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 424.4pt; border: 1pt solid windowtext; background: rgb(0__kanma__ 176__kanma__ 240); padding: 0mm 5.4pt;"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box;">ネット銀行<span lang="EN-US" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-all; line-height: 28